	<description>
		<![CDATA[<b>AutoArm</b>

<b>Core features:</b>
• Add weapons to outfit filters just like apparel
• Colonists automatically equip better weapons based on their skills
• Respects player choice - manually equipped weapons are remembered

<b>How to Use:</b>
1. Open a colonist's outfit policy
2. You'll see a new "Weapons" category under Apparel
3. Allow/disallow specific weapons or entire categories
4. Colonists will automatically manage their weapons according to the policy

<b>Load Order:</b>
• Before: Performance mods and AI behavior mods. Auto-sort handles most cases.

Report issues at the workshop]]>
	</description>
